data.description: WOW!!! A 3.25% VA Loan that is assumable.... Experience unparalleled luxury in this 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom masterpiece spanning 3,829 sqft, destined to be the crown jewel of Winchester, CA. Nestled in the scenic Dutch Valley, within the prestigious Vista Del Valle community crafted by Capital Pacific Homes, this residence is situated in the acclaimed Murrieta Valley School District.    Convenience meets leisure with proximity to Diamond Valley Lake, the Western Science Center, and Lake Skinner Recreation Area. Immerse yourself in the charm of Temecula Wineries just 25 minutes away, while enjoying easy access to Oceanside in 1 hour, San Diego in 1hr 20min, and Los Angeles in 1.5 hours. Elevate your lifestyle in this meticulously designed home at the heart of Southern California's sought-after destinations.
